| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1455 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8d408cf6-453a-5f06-b20c-e7c21800ad16"
